{
  "id": "earl",
  "name": "EARL",
  "color": "#d3699e",
  "lore": {
    "tagline": "They call EARL.",
    "personality": "Curator of soundly unsound sounds, and an off-the-wagon recovering musician.",
    "backstory": "Known in a past life as The Madd WIkkid. Mars adjacent since 2020, first time Martian 2026. Teaching music theory. Has an excessive amount of field recording gear. Expert at most things audio. Plays piano, trumpet, and a little bass. Produced and engineered records for a couple of decades. Toured Japan playing piano with a Japanese gospel choir. Expert at technical sound design and was an audio director for AAA games for a while. Getting back to music after a long haitus. Creating a fictional band here on Mars with cartoon band members called The Unhung Zeros. Considers fetishization of proces to be antithetical to the creation of great art. Used to trade stock on Wall Street during the dotcom bubble. Was selected as a mentor to TED fellows. Does not abide charlatainism."
  },
  "winQuotes": [
    "EARL wins. That's music to my ears...",
    "This was the rehearsal. You should come to the gig.",
    "You'll never be a star."
  ],
